      * L10: 001000 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      * L11: 001100     ACCEPT X.
      * L12: 001200     ACCEPT Y.
      * L13: 001300     IF (X <= Y)
      * L14: 001400         MOVE X TO S
      * L15: 001500     ELSE
      * L16: 001600         MOVE Y TO S.
